<tr><td nowrap width="20%" valign=baseline align=right><b>Notable Features: </b></td><td colspan=4 align=left valign=baseline>One ball per play. <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Trap_Hole">Trap&nbsp;holes</a> (29). Two <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Outhole">outholes</a>.</td></tr>
<tr><td nowrap width="20%" valign=baseline align=right><b>Notes: </b></td><td colspan=4 align=left valign=baseline>The name of this game is not found on the <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Backglass">backglass</a> but is located at the very top of the <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Playfield">playfield</a>.<br><br>The non-payout version of this game is <span title="Click here to open a new window and display Bally's 1940 'Dark Horse'"><a target="game638" href="machine.cgi?id=638">Bally's 1940 'Dark Horse'</a></span>.<P></td></tr>
